{"tid":2250356,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"英國首相約翰遜: 打算明年初辭職  人工太低  僅得15萬英鎊","createTime":"2020-10-20T05:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:40:27.000Z","uid":66271,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a70b8905ec97a5472a4a1b6e3fbe52740c2e882e","tid":2250356,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"英國《大都市報》（Metro）引述消息人士指，英國首相約翰遜有意在明年初辭職，因為約翰遜認為自己出任首相的年薪僅得15萬英鎊（約151萬港元），人工比他出任首相前更低，由於約翰遜不但要撫養6個小孩，而且要向前妻支付一大筆離婚費用，因此出任首相的年薪不足以生活，令他有財政負擔。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，約翰遜擔任首相之前，曾在《電訊報》撰寫專欄，每月可賺2.3萬英鎊（約23萬港元），他亦會不時應邀發表演說，可賺數以十萬計英鎊。據《鏡報》早前報道，約翰遜在一個月內發表過兩次演說，共可賺16萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n《大都市報》的報道又指，約翰遜希望在半年內解決英國脫歐僵局，並帶英國成功抵抗疫情，然後辭職。"},{"pid":"ef182ab0600a6018a5f0d2386be5790f39951977","tid":2250356,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"消息人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeb22e8fc684dfbbaf4c5b932d16b1b2c34c7bf","tid":2250356,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"約翰遜+U<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4910c4412288446ca058cada455755c704f3b918","tid":2250356,"uid":195690,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"做首相為左養家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到自己好似都係打份工咁"},{"pid":"fa74c8118c7ce4aebb5a09e404729b0c8b10e40a","tid":2250356,"uid":134415,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"打份工唔係為錢唔通為興趣咩!"},{"pid":"48f804eeb5aaa259ec339e262568075ab9809c74","tid":2250356,"uid":10757,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O09ws3p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F